50|$|Haavara (Transfer) Ltd. was {{a company}} founded {{as a result}} of the Haavara Agreement made during <b>the</b> <b>Nazi</b> <b>regime's</b> control over Germany. The company {{facilitated}} the emigration of approximately 50,000 Jews from Germany to Palestine.|$|R
